databases are a kind of storage house

we can store all our data in our data

its of two types relational and non relational

RELATIONAL->SQL which is more schemed-->MySQL-->less scalable(vertically)

NON RELATIONAL->NOSQL which is more flexible-->MongoDB-->highly scalable(horizontally)

#OPERATIONS TO BE PERFORMED

1.create
2.read
3.update
4.delete

also known as CRUD

